" set statusline="%= %A %10u:%-7g %15s %20d  "

" Total size of selected files
" To get the total size of selected files change %s to %E in ~/.vifm/vifmrc, like so:
set statusline="  %t%= %A %10u:%-7g %15E %20d  "

